title: Frank Lloyd Wright Glass Panel—Water Lilies
description:
Water Lilies, 1895 by Frank Lloyd Wright® (American, 1867–1959) .  This tranquil art glass panel is adapted from an unrealized stained glass window designed by Wright in 1895. Copper patina frame with wood stand.  

Includes 11 in. chain for hanging. 

5 1/8 x 15 in.
